  <!-- Description -->
  <description>
    Comet Games Studio is an indie game developer focused on creating immersive space exploration and cosmic horror experiences. Our team combines scientific accuracy with imaginative storytelling to craft unique gaming experiences that challenge players' perspectives of the universe.
  </description>

  <!-- History -->
  <histories>
    <history>
      <header>The Big Bang (2022)</header>
      <text>Founded by former NASA scientist Dr. Sarah Chen and veteran game developer Marcus Wong, Comet Games Studio began with a simple mission: to make space exploration games that are both scientifically accurate and incredibly fun.</text>
    </history>
    <history>
      <header>First Light (2023)</header>
      <text>Released our first game, "Stellar Drift," which earned critical acclaim for its innovative zero-gravity mechanics and atmospheric storytelling. The game was featured at PAX West and won the "Best New Studio" award at IndieCade.</text>
    </history>
    <history>
      <header>Expanding Universe (2024)</header>
      <text>Grew from a team of 2 to 15 passionate developers, artists, and scientists. Opened our new studio in downtown Seattle with a built-in planetarium for inspiration.</text>
    </history>
  </histories>

